fix 	m3 all property/global coefficientRestitution peratomtypepair 2 0.7 0.7 0.7 0.7
fix 	m4 all property/global coefficientFriction peratomtypepair 2 ${FRIC} ${FRICPW} ${FRICPW} ${FRICPW}
fix 	m4 all property/global coefficientFriction peratomtypepair 2 0.2652 ${FRICPW} ${FRICPW} ${FRICPW}
